  "text": "In all, 98 features are extracted to represent the visual properties of the region, of which 84 features (color, texture, structure and moments) are used for sites. For objects and events, all 98 features are used. A similar set/subset of features can also be obtained at the global level without segmentation and also on difference frames obtained using successive consecutive frames [CITATION_1] .",
